{"tid":2051173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【六四事件】中國取巨大成就 外交部：證明當年行動完全正確","createTime":"2020-06-04T14:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T15:30:35.000Z","uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7ca6d247358ee2d0694b2b90049ce7b5c59153","tid":2051173,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fyrfku1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffyrfku1.jpg&h=b6846fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【六四事件】中國取巨大成就 外交部：證明當年行動完全正確<br />\n環球政經 21:00 2020/06/04<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國外文部發言人趙立堅重申，對於上世紀八十年代末發生的政治風波，中國政府早有明確結論，又指中國的巨大發展成就，表明中國政府當時採取的行動是完全正確，令國家政治穩定、經濟發展與社會進步，得以維護及繼續。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞: 【六四事件】連續31年發聲明 佩洛西：北京侵犯人權三十年<br />\n<br />\n他又指，中國人民將堅定不移的，沿著中國特色社會主義道路不斷前進，敦促美方摒棄意識形態偏見，糾正錯誤，並停止干預中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n撰文 : 國際組<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2661952/%E3%80%90%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%96%E5%B7%A8%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%20%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%EF%BC%9A%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA</code></pre>"},{"pid":"1757b93b5cdc1894369632eca312b6d171532ea2","tid":2051173,"uid":231583,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"中國取巨大成就 外交部：證明當年南京大屠殺完全正確"},{"pid":"3c9efc41bacaef19203323e41e8547792d81ce50","tid":2051173,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1757b93b5cdc1894369632eca312b6d171532ea2","tid":2051173,"uid":231583,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"中國取巨大成就 外交部：證明當年南京大屠殺完全正確"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"多難興邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a638223435062f2abc5cb23313523cdba915b7","tid":2051173,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T14: